# lint-github-workflow

Linter for GitHub Workflow definitions.

## Development

### Build

Build with Poetry:

```shell
poetry build
```

Run with your favorite shell:

```bash
./bin/ghwflint
```

### Release

Publish to PyPI with Twine:

```shell
twine upload dist/ghwflint-*-none-any.whl
```

